  "id": "pulseboard",
  "channels": ["pulseboard"],
  "configSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {}
  }
}
```

Pattern: identical to `extensions/irc/openclaw.plugin.json` with id swapped.

---

### 3. `extensions/pulseboard/src/types.ts`

Three exported interfaces — no imports needed.

```ts
export interface PulseBoardAccount {
  boardUrl: string;
  apiToken: string;
  username: string;
}

