### 4. `extensions/pulseboard/src/runtime.ts`

Mirrors `extensions/nostr/src/runtime.ts`. Uses an inline `PluginRuntime` type
rather than a separate `runtime-api.ts` barrel (since PulseBoard has no
runtime-injected functions beyond the empty store slot).

